              ┌ Keybindings ─────────────────────────────┐
              │ Help                                     │
              │                                          │
              │ Navigation                               │
              │  j/k  or  Up/Down      Move selection    │
              │  [ / ]                  Scroll up / down │
              │by page_size rows                         │
              │  g / G                  Go to first /    │
              │last row                                  │
              │  Ctrl+g                 Search cached    │
              │views (all tabs)                          │
              │  1–6                    Jump to view tab │
              │  7–9                    Custom JQL views │
              │(if configured)                           │
              │  v / Shift+V            Cycle custom     │
              │views                                     │
              │  Shift+E                Manage templates │
              └──────────────────────────────────────────┘
